            . The prisoner bought a fowl of me for eighteen-pence. A girl informed me he put off bad money; he came again in half an hour and agreed for another fowl; he offered me 5 s. 3 d. I took it to Mr. Collins; he said it was bad, and came out and secured the prisoner.</p>
