               <p>- Brand. I am a constable: I was sent for by Mr. Collins; he gave me charge of the prisoner; I took him into a back room and searched him; I found ten shillings upon him.</p>
               <p>(They were produced as well as the quarter of a guinea, and proved to be all counterfeit.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner in his defence called one witness, who knew him two years ago, who said he had a good character then.</p>
